ActCanadian Wheat Board Act
PrecisAuthority for the CANADIAN WHEAT BOARD (a) to adjust its accounts as of December 31, 2008, by transferring the undistributed funds in the 2001-2002 pool accounts for wheat and amber durum wheat to a separate account; and (b) to pay to the persons who are entitled to receive payments the amount to which they are entitled out of the separate account.
